window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Only a few years ago, I was a mage in a world filled with magic and supernatural creatures. Now, I'm in a world where science has made people into superpowered titans. As the only mage in this world, I'm using my talismans and spells to even the odds.</p> <p>Working as a private investigator, I'm hunting down leads on what landed me among the supers. But I'm not the only supernatural creature who showed up here, and it's a problem that's about to get out of hand.</p> <p>Science vs. Magic. It's a battle that's bound to turn this world upside down.</p> <p>It's a good thing I have a brilliantly minded blonde lawyer and a feisty superpowered heroine on my side.</p>"; 
